    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical work to be roadworthy again. The engine has a pronounced knock and frequently stalls, while the transmission exhibits severe slipping in higher gears. Externally, the car shows its age with several large dents, peeling clear coat, and visible rust on the rocker panels. The interior is heavily worn with torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. This is a project car or a candidate for parts, sold strictly as-is.",
